{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like there was now immediately a council was organized, Germans saw to it that the councils were organized.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that council actually governed the day-to-day life in the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were new-- new order, new edicts issued.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Naturally, everybody had to start getting a card.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Food started getting rationed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you had to get coupons, you had to get a card from the council.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Committees were formed and the Germans all through this here walked day in and day out the neighborhoods and were just shooting people for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The slightest transgression and you were shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we could see this here, so naturally, anybody they thought who would try to escape or do some funny things had a second thought.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We realized how serious the situation is and how tragic it is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And hoping and praying that someday this is going to stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But instead, things started getting from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not a free election.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans appointed whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was former-- former Jewish community active people that were put on and then a host of other people who, by their own initiative, or by their own doings, became leaders.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those leaders later on in the later years-- in '41, '42, '43-- they became kings because they-- they were deciding upon death and life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans have requested from them to deliver so many Jews per month or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And naturally, they made up the lists and they were the ones who sent out the Jewish militia, which was formed by the council to pick up these people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, there were all kinds of ways of getting out of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, everybody had to be working and have an ID card.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
